### **4. 25_RealTimeChartMaker**  
**Description:**  
A Python tool to visualize numeric input as a real-time chart.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealTimeChartMaker - Live Graph Plotting Tool

RealTimeChartMaker plots dynamic data on a Matplotlib-powered live chart. Great for demos, simulations, or sensors.

## Features
- Live updates  
- Custom stream frequency  
- Clean UI  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/25_RealTimeChartMaker.git
cd 25_RealTimeChartMaker
python visualize.py
